Title: Reject configuration on missing timeperiod
Component: config
Class: bug
State: done
Date: 2014-11-17 11:11:51
Targetversion: next

If a host or service has been assigned a missing timeperiod
then the core segfaults when this timeperiod is being queried.
The configuration enginge must make sure that all referred-to
timeperiods are defined.

